      "chunk_id": "8d3b59024d023001_0028",
      "text": "7.1. Neither of the Parties make any express or implied representation or warranty as to the accuracy, reliability or completeness of the Confidential Information, expressly disclaiming any and all liability that may be based on the Confidential Information, including any errors therein or omissions there from.",
