      "text": "12.5. Severance. If any provision of this Agreement is or becomes invalid or unenforceable, it shall be deemed modified to the minimum extent necessary to make it valid and enforceable. Any modification to a provision under this clause shall not affect the validity and enforceability of the rest of the Agreement.",
